### Crear parche de tarifa
POST http://localhost:8000/patch_tariff
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "route_from": "MAD",
  "route_to": "BCN",
  "service_type": "groupage",
  "weight_range": {"min": 0, "max": 1000},
  "target_field": "precio",
  "operacion": "percent_up",
  "valor": 5,
  "nota": "Incremento temporal",
  "autor": "operaciones"
}

### Calcular tarifa
POST http://localhost:8000/get_tariff
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "origen": "MAD",
  "destino": "BCN",
  "tipo_servicio": "groupage",
  "peso": 500,
  "precio_base": 1000
}

